data.text:
Georgios Karagounis prefers to play with right foot. His jersey number is 21.

Georgios Karagounis career statistics, match ratings, heatmap and goals are available on Sofascore for current and previous seasons. Last player match was Costa Rica - Greece (6 - 4) and Georgios Karagounis received 8 Sofascore rating.

If Georgios Karagounis plays you will also be able to follow his live Sofascore rating, statistics and heatmap. Georgios Karagounis football player profile displays all matches and competitions with statistics for all the matches Georgios Karagounis played in. Most important stats for each competition, including average Sofascore rating, matches played, goals, assists, cards and other relevant data are also displayed.
